The COSAFA tournaments have been severely impacted by the Covid-19 pandemic but the organisation said that it is "hopeful that it will be able to host four other tournaments this year." Women's teams from Tanzania, Botswana and Zimbabwe, who is still awaiting permission to travel, are among those that will participate in the tournament that will kick off on November 3-14 in South Africa at the Eastern Cape region's Nelson Mandela Bay.  --AllAfrica--